.TH devin-setup 1  "setup " 
.SH NAME
devin\-setup \- Interactive setup wizard
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdevin setup\fR [\fB\-\-force\-manual\-token\-flow\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Interactive setup wizard
.PP
Guides you through authentication, shell integration, and MCP configuration.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-force\-manual\-token\-flow\fR
Skip browser\-based auth and paste a token manually

Useful for remote or SSH sessions where the localhost redirect won\*(Aqt work.
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
